PeopleHighlightsUpcomingMeeting.commandText: Summarize due action items or tasks between {people} and me from email, chats, files and meetings in the last 14 days only. For each task include: brief description; priority; and source link (e.g. email, chat, file, meeting). ALWAYS only show tasks that include direct interaction between me and {people} - where {people} or I have been @mentioned, addressed or assigned the task by either of us. In tabular format separate tasks {people} owes me from tasks I owe {people} and order by priority. Suggest next actions I should take.
